{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"db22597f5e","title":"人民大学教师决心割毒瘤","origin":"美国图书馆收藏","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ed6218373c","index":0,"year":1958,"month":4,"day":1,"articleId":"db22597f5e"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"93741cb486","name":"吴振全"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4ce276a174","type":"title","text":"贵州各地在兴修水利中不断发生火药爆炸事故","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"db22597f5e"},{"id":"79a3bc1421","type":"authors","text":"吴振全","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"db22597f5e"},{"id":"cd3d8adf66","type":"paragraph","text":"新华社贵阳3日讯　贵州省各地今春兴修水利中，由于对购置的炸药管理不善，不断发生爆炸事故，造成重大伤亡和财产损失。如遵义县上溪镇供销社，3月23日发生黑色炸药爆炸事故，死伤九十七人，供销社的财产全部烧光，损失折款一万多元。兴义县桔山乡，也因不慎发生火药爆炸事故，死伤二十多人。类似这样事件，在大方、均匀、毕节等县都有发生。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"db22597f5e"},{"id":"3ff64316f9","type":"paragraph","text":"以上严重情况，已引起中共贵州省委的注意。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"db22597f5e"},{"id":"291332b984","type":"paragraph","text":"来源：1958年4月9日新华通讯社编《内部参考》。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"db22597f5e"}],"page":{"id":"59ebdc49d0","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"db22597f5e","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}